  <section id="troubleshooting" class="scroll-mt-24" data-animate>
    <p class="mb-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-bipbip-red">Support</p>
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-neutral-900 dark:text-white">
      Troubleshooting
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
      The four most frequently asked questions during integration. If you cannot find the answer here,
